General Information
===================

This is version 0.1.0 of wide. Wide stand for Well Integrated Development Environment.

wide is released under the GNU General Public License (GPL) version 2 or
later, see the file 'COPYING' for more information.

Installation
============

Simple install procedure:

  % git clone https://github.com/christian-brunello/wide.git # clone repository
  % cd wide				# change to the toplevel directory
	% autoreconf    # create build tools
  % ./configure		# run the `configure' script
  % make					# build wide
  [ Become root if necessary ]
  % make install	# install wide

See the file 'INSTALL' for more detailed information.


How to report bugs
==================

Bugs should be reported to the github repository.

Patches
=======

Please create patches with the git format-patch command.

If you are interested in helping us to develop gedit, please see the 
file 'AUTHOR' for contact information.


  The wide team.
